Vigenere Cipher

Matn Base64 bilan kodlangan.

Decode qilinganda UTF-8 belgilar ketma-ketligi chiqadi.

So‘ng bu belgilar Vigenere usuli bilan shifrlangan.

py code: 

import base64

s = "wqbDksKkeMOEw4bDgHXCpnjCkcOOwrxTwqzCk8KzwojCqVPCncKZwqjCn8OTw5rDq2bCmGPClMKywpRow5fCq8KoZcOIZsKXwrLCmWTCpMOWwqZpw4TCmcOJwq7DhmTCpMOZwqDCmcKYwrA="
key = "cyb3rsp4c3"

cipher = base64.b64decode(s).decode("utf-8")

plain = ''.join(
    chr((ord(c) - ord(key[i % len(key)])) % 256)
    for i, c in enumerate(cipher)
)

print(plain)

